  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and so you kind of grew with it and you had to defend yourself sometimes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was something that you grow with, and something that becomes a normal existence, and you cope with it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the answer to your question is yes, there was-- there was definitely that kind of a harassment during my childhood years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the adults-- there was always-- there was always problems on an adult basis also, because when we heard our elders-- our older-- be it uncles or friends and so on, there was also always a tale that they had a confrontation and-- and they were harassed, stopped, beaten, or-- or called down on-- on the basis of their religion.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was a normal-- it was a normal' existence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- I don't recall that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- I-- I can't say that, that the-- that the teachers did or the-- I just think educated people are basically not prone to do that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my cheder was a typical cheder, where the rabbi had the long beard and the little bone [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] indicator, whatever you call it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you didn't prepare-- if you didn't prepare for your lesson, you got a nice little slap, or a little patsh here and a little patsh there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And today, as I look back, it wasn't so terrible, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you were scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you weren't prepared and you played, sort of, hooky for your next lesson, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they let you know in no uncertain terms that-- I'm talking in the physical ways, that next time you'd better come prepared.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
